    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are acknowledged as not-assessed per MRL 2 scoping rules, with Gradation 1 requirements satisfied for each. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index predictions are within acceptable agreement with experimental data across all 5 operating points. COU1 assessment accepted.",
